Задание 3: Факторизация
def prime_factor(n):
    answer = []
    while n % 2 == 0:
        answer.append(2)
        n //= 2
    for i in range(3, int(n**0.5) + 1, 2):
        while n % i == 0:
            answer.append(i)
            n //= i
    if n > 1:
        answer.append(n)
    return answer
Сложность O(n**0.5), память O(logn)


